## Timeline Estimation Rules

### ❌ WRONG (Human Development Timelines)
```
v3.0.0: Clean Architecture restructuring (3-4 weeks)
v3.1.0: Enhanced matching (2-3 weeks)
Total: 18-23 weeks for human team
```

### ✅ CORRECT (Agentic AI Timelines)
```
v3.0.0: Clean Architecture restructuring (1-2 days AI work)
v3.1.0: Enhanced matching (1 day AI work)
Total: 10-15 days of AI-driven implementation
```

