## Estimation Guidelines

| Task Complexity | Human Team | AI Agent (Multi-Persona) |
|----------------|------------|--------------------------|
| Simple feature | 1-2 weeks | 1-2 hours |
| Medium feature | 2-4 weeks | 1-2 days |
| Large feature | 1-2 months | 3-5 days |
| Architecture refactor | 3-4 weeks | 1-2 days |
| Full system (6 versions) | 6 months | 10-15 days |

**Why AI is Faster:**
- No meetings, no coordination overhead
- No context switching between developers
- Instant access to entire codebase
- Can work on multiple files simultaneously
- Immediate test feedback loops
- No deployment delays (local Docker)

